reviewText: I own the VHS of this and I used to watch it quite frequently, however the quality of the DVD, in my opinion, is worse than my VHS, it makes me feel like I should just keep my old DVD/VCR combo in order to watch it with better quality.
Love this almost as much as Saturdays Warriors

I have liked this movie ever since my mom found it somewhere and i first watched it.  I am really happy that i found it for myself and that it is on DVD. Thank you very much for helping me find it easy.
